title: "CogSecSkills: Multiharness Agentic Skills for Cognitive Security"
abstract: >-
  A defensive, educational, harness-neutral library of 100 agentic tool-use
  skills for Cognitive Security and analytic tradecraft — Structured Analytic
  Techniques, source verification, deception detection, and critical review —
  each runnable identically under Claude Code, Codex, and Hermes, with a
  registry, an AGEINT educational upstream, and machine-checkable conformance.
